uirements. Furthermore, at least 0.9 cache hit rate is\nrequired to satisfy all flows for at least 50% of simulated flights.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Apr 2020 15:15:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-02"}
